Description: Free Pico clone with some new features (dev)
License: GPL
Maintainer: Andreas Gockel <fink-nano@unixforge.de>
Depends: libncursesw5-shlibs (>= 5.4-20041023-1001), libiconv, libgettext3-shlibs
